snippet.title: #43 || Warner Bros. Screwed Up
snippet.description:
One of the biggest news recently in Hollywood is probably the news about Johnny Depp being asked to leave Fantastic Beats 3 as Grindelwald but his ex-wife, Amber Heard was allowed to stay on for DC movies like Aquaman. Isn't that crazy? The Judge from the court case even threw out Johnny Depp's evidence even though it was a recording of Amber Heard admitting to hitting Johnny Depp. Hollywood is weird. But Warner Bros. did Johnny Depp dirty... Funny enough though, Warner Bros. still has to pay Johnny Depp his 8-figure salary even though he only filmed one scene in the movie.
